### Notice Regarding Pre-trained AI Models & ONNX Weights / モデルおよびONNXのライセンスに関する注意点

This repository contains source code only and does NOT include any pre-trained model weights.

- The source code of this project is licensed under the MIT License.
- However, third-party pre-trained models and ONNX weights (e.g., Essentia models, Discogs classifiers, Demucs models) fetched or utilized by this tool are subject to their respective original licenses (e.g., AGPLv3 for Essentia models by MTG/UPF, CC BY-NC-SA 4.0, MIT, etc.).
- Users are solely responsible for complying with the licensing terms of any third-party models or ONNX files downloaded and executed with this software, especially regarding commercial use and redistribution.

